'''Samantha Biffot''' (wavutse 1985) ni umwanditsi wa sinema wa [[Gabon]]-[[Igifaransa]], utunganya amafilime akaba n'umuyobozi wa firime<ref>Biffot, Samantha | African Film Festival, Inc. <nowiki>https://africanfilmny.org</nowiki> › directors › samantha-biffot</ref>.

== Ubuzima ==
Biffot yavukiye i [[Paris]] mu 1985. Yabayeho mu bwana bwe hagati ya [[Gabon]], [[Koreya y’Amajyepfo|Koreya]] y'Epfo [[Ubufaransa|n'Ubufaransa]], kandi uburere bwe butandukanye bwagize imico myinshi nyuma yo gukina film<ref>Samantha Biffot - Fiche Personne sur Africultures <nowiki>http://africultures.com</nowiki> › personnes</ref>.  Amaze kubona impamyabumenyi ye, yize muri École Supérieure de Réalisation Audiovisuelle i [[Paris]] aho yakuye impamyabumenyi ya sinema mu 2007<ref>Samantha Biffot, creator of the series Mami Wata - Canneseries <nowiki>https://canneseries.com</nowiki> › online › samantha-biffot-creator...</ref>. Amashuri arangije, Biffot yarangije kwimenyereza gukora kuri  televiziyo na firime nyinshi mu [[Bufaransa]]<ref>Samantha Biffot - | Diversity of Cultural Expressions <nowiki>https://en.unesco.org</nowiki> › capacity-building › experts</ref>. Biffot yasubiye muri  [[Gabon]] mu 2010 aho yashinze isosiyete ya  "Princesse M Production" hamwe na Pierre-Adrien Ceccaldi<ref>Samantha Biffot | Neon Red Production <nowiki>https://tact-production.com</nowiki> › samantha-biffot</ref>. Mu mwaka wa 2011, yateguye amahugurwa mu kwerekana amashusho, gukora, gushushanya no gutunganya mu rwego mpuzamahanga mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga ry’inkiko z’ishuri i Libreville.<ref>Samantha Biffot | Berlinale Talents <nowiki>https://www.berlinale-talents.de</nowiki> › talent › profile</ref> 

Mu mwaka wa 2013, televiziyo ye ''L'Œil de la cité'' (Ijisho ry'umujyi) yahawe igihembo cy'uruhererekane rwiza rwa [[Afurika]] mu Iserukiramuco rya Filime na Televiziyo bya Panafrican ya Ouagadougou<ref>Samantha Biffot - Serieseries.tv <nowiki>https://www.serieseries.tv</nowiki> › person › cast-276 › samanth...</ref> .  Uruhererekane rwasuzumye ibyaha by’imihango n’ibibazo by’ibidukikije n’imibereho, buri gice kigira imyitwarire irangiye<ref>Directors - Samantha Biffot - ARDECHE IMAGES <nowiki>http://www.lussasdoc.org</nowiki> › rea-sama...</ref>. Yavuze ko yayobowe nuruhererekane ''rwabanyamerika Tales kuva muri Crypt'', kandi urukurikirane rwe rwakozwe na Institut Gabonais de l'Image et du Son<ref>Samantha Biffot remporte le 2e prix de la meilleure série <nowiki>https://www.union.sonapresse.com</nowiki> › ...</ref>.  Mu mwaka wa 2016, Biffot yasohoye documentaire Africa Who Wanted to fly, yerekana ubuzima bwa shebuja wa Gabon kung fu, Luc Bendza . Iyi filime yahawe igihembo cyihariye cy’abacamanza mu iserukiramuco Escales Socumentaires de Libreville ndetse no kuba Filime Nziza  mu Iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga ry'i [[Burundi]] mu mwaka wa 2017<ref>Samantha Biffot représentera le Gabon aux Africa Movie ... <nowiki>https://gaboncelebrites.com</nowiki> › samant...</ref>.  ''Africa Who Wanted to fly'' yanerekanwe muri Internationales Dokumentarfilmf Festival München no mu iserukiramuco rya sinema nyafurika ryabereye i New York.<ref>“L'Africain qui voulait voler”, le documentaire de Samantha ... (gaboncelebrites.com)</ref> 

